DefectAware Agent

This project is based on and substantially extends the CSAagentGA project:
https://github.com/maincourses/CSAagentGA

The upstream project authors have granted permission for public redistribution.
The Git history is preserved to retain authorship and contribution attribution.

Major additions in this repository include Agent evaluation, a controlled
multi-agent workflow, SQLite/FastAPI observability, evidence verification,
structured-output validation, reliability controls, and checkpoint recovery.
